description: This file serves as the entry point for a React application. It imports React and ReactDOM libraries, along with CSS styling and the main App component. It creates a root DOM node and renders the App component wrapped in React's StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering a React component tree in a specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders a React element into the root.
